{"id": "Stand van TMT december 2019__c4-paragraph__0006", "text": "The economic climate is deteriorating in the Netherlands. The purchasing managers’ index (PMI), producer confidence and consumer confidence have declined in recent quarters. Even so, entrepreneurs in the TMT sector are relatively positive compared with business as a whole.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT december 2019__c4-paragraph__0006", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT december 2019", "source_title": "State of TMT December 2019", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 6, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT december 2019__c4-paragraph__0007", "text": "What is affecting the TMT sector is a shortage of staff. No fewer than 33% of TMT entrepreneurs say they cannot obtain the required workforce. The shortage is particularly acute in IT. There, 41% of entrepreneurs struggle to find suitable staff.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT december 2019__c4-paragraph__0007", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT december 2019", "source_title": "State of TMT December 2019", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 7, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
{"id": "Stand van TMT december 2019__c4-paragraph__0008", "text": "Read our forecasts in the full report ‘State of TMT’.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "Stand van TMT december 2019__c4-paragraph__0008", "source_slug": "Stand van TMT december 2019", "source_title": "State of TMT December 2019", "source_url": null, "source_date": null, "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": null, "topic": null, "language_original": null, "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "gpt-5", "translated_with": null, "chunker": "c4-paragraph", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 14, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-05-06"}}
